data.description: Enjoy this modest yet inviting 3-bedroom, 1.5 bath home with wrap around deck, complete with a 30x40 heated shop/garage.  Use the heated shop, with 220V outlets, for all your projects and storage needs, plus a sauna fur luxurious relaxation. The additional studio dwelling, though unfinished, offers potential for customization to suit your preferences.   The property is fully fenced with access gates on 3 sides, mature trees and a storage shed.  Don't wait to make this exceptional property your own!
